title: New Excalibur
description:
By request from the forums. This Torrent contains MarvelComics New Excalibur and X-Men: Die by the Sword; the two most recent series featuring the Excalibur team originally rendered by Alan Davis.

New Excalibur ran from early 2006 through the end of 2007. The earliest issues were part of the X-men "Decimation" stroy line. X-men: Die by the Sword was a four issue follow-up published in early 2008 on the coat-tails of the New Excalibur series.

Thanks to the scanners and the original and varied sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
